description:
James DiEugenio, author of 'The JFK Assassination: The Evidence Today' (https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07B1LVJPK)  discusses the latest evidence in the J.D. Tippit case.

Read more about this in Jim's detailed article on Kennedys and King, 'The Tippit Case in the New Millennium'. (https://kennedysandking.com/john-f-kennedy-articles/919)
